{
  "stem": "27150.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you see, it sets up with my good luck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, somebody invented pantyhose, because most of the girdles were worn to keep the stockings up, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, Lola got sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- well, I was sitting in the hospital, and I gave to my two managers, you see, the plenipotentiary or the right to sign, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were very good to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your place is not here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your place is in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually, you see, the whole business wound up, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I came to my regular thing, and they started-- they presented me with a bill.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To think I thought it was charity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was cunningness.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, I was three years on my own, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That means I sold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that means we were doing, you know-- because you see, other than girdles, we were doing, you see, elastics for Johnson Brothers, and things--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not especially.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- my friends were all Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we lived in [INAUDIBLE] next door to-- to better [INAUDIBLE] the college.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Ann went to college, and I was taking her to the Sunday school, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I belonged to B'nai B'rith, and all my friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the good old days, I was donating more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I reduced my donation, and I live on my savings.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
